<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idf662928c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1984-04-15">Apr. 15, 1984</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/98/89/s2/g/1">section 2(g)(1) of Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t46/s3101">section 3101 of this title</ref>.</p>
